---
// Final whitelist CTA. The form submit is intercepted (demo) in app.js.
---

<section class="section" id="join">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="final reveal">
      <span class="live-pill" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><span class="dot beat"></span><span data-i18n="hero_badge">En vivo · Latencia &lt; 200 ms</span></span>
      <h2 data-i18n="final_title">Sumate a la whitelist.</h2>
      <p class="lead" data-i18n="final_sub">Estamos abriendo acceso por tandas. Dejanos tu email y sé de los primeros en hablar sin barreras.</p>
      <form class="wl-form" data-wl-form>
        <input type="email" required data-i18n-ph="final_ph" placeholder="tu@email.com" aria-label="Email" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-i18n="final_btn">Unirme a la whitelist</button>
      </form>
      <div class="final-note">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3 5 6v5c0 4.5 3 8 7 10 4-2 7-5.5 7-10V6z" /><path d="M9.5 12l1.8 1.8L15 9.8" /></svg>
        <span data-i18n="final_note">Acceso anticipado · Sin spam · Cancelás cuando quieras</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
